title: JAL Restart Special Aircraft Service in JapanTravelandtourworld.com
text:
JAL restart special aircraft service in Japan Published on : Thursday, July 9, 2015
Japan Airlines Co., Ltd. (JAL) and Oriental Land Co., Ltd. (Oriental Land) announced a collaboration for the Tokyo DisneySea special program “Journeys with Duffy: Your Friend Forever.” The specially painted aircraft “JAL Happy Journey Express” (Boeing 737-800 series) will begin domestic flights starting July 14, 2015. The aircraft will feature an illustration of Duffy the Disney Bear, a Tokyo DisneySea character, on its exterior.
JAL, an official sponsor of Tokyo DisneySea Park since it opened, and Oriental Land developed this plan specifically to mark the ten years since Duffy’s debut at Tokyo DisneySea Park. Guests are sure to enjoy flying on this unique Duffy-decorated aircraft.
Source:- JAL
